joke_list.joke: A blind man walks into a bar. And a table. And a chair.
What's orange and sounds like a parrot? A carrot.
What do you call a black guy flying a plane? A pilot, you fucking racist.
The bartender says, "We don't serve time travelers here." A time traveler walks into a bar.
What do you call an alligator in a vest? An Investigator.
What's the difference between swine flu and bird flu? Bird flu requires tweetment, and swine flu requires oinkment!
